  <brief_title>Fentanyl 12 Mcg Transdermal Patch For Postoperative Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect Of Fentanyl 12 Mcg Transdermal Patch On Postoperative Pain Following Unilateral, Single-Level Laminectomy/Discectomy: A Randomized, Controlled, Double-Blind Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
