  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators designed a prospective randomized study to investigate the effect of
      fentanyl 12 mcg transdermal patch on postoperative pain following unilateral, single-level
      laminectomy/discectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
